{"data":{"page":{"id":"f786caec-7c82-550f-a096-c24fea4724ac","html":"<p class=\"align-center\">\n<a class=\"btn\" href=\"http://momardi.com\" target=\"_blank\">Launch website</a>\n<a class=\"btn\" href=\"http://momardi-wp.herokuapp.com/\" target=\"_blank\">Launch archived v1 website</a>\n</p>\n<p><span\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-wrapper\"\n    style=\"position: relative; display: block;  max-width: 960px; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto;\"\n  >\n    <span\n      class=\"gatsby-resp-image-background-image\"\n      style=\"padding-bottom: 56.666666666666664%; position: relative; bottom: 0; left: 0; background-image: url('data:image/jpeg;base64,'); background-size: cover; display: block;\"\n    ></span>\n    <img\n        class=\"gatsby-resp-image-image\"\n        style=\"width:100%;height:100%;margin:0;vertical-align:middle;position:absolute;top:0;left:0;box-shadow:inset 0px 0px 0px 400px transparent;\"\n        alt=\"1\"\n        title=\"\"\n        src=\"/static/3e53665fe627633e3a19172772d0c6f2/89cd4/1.jpg\"\n        srcset=\"/static/3e53665fe627633e3a19172772d0c6f2/80bba/1.jpg 500w,\n/static/3e53665fe627633e3a19172772d0c6f2/89cd4/1.jpg 960w\"\n        sizes=\"(max-width: 960px) 100vw, 960px\"\n      />\n  </span></p>\n<p>I built Momardi.com initially with a custom template for Wordpress, but after a couple of years, we moved it into the Ghost platform and built another custom theme. And then, after a few more years, I moved to a GatsbyJS platform.</p>\n<p>Momardi is the personal website of Tuesday Gutierrez. It showcases art exhibits in galleries / museums and also features articles about new artists.</p>\n<p><span\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-wrapper\"\n    style=\"position: relative; display: block;  max-width: 1000px; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto;\"\n  >\n    <span\n      class=\"gatsby-resp-image-background-image\"\n      style=\"padding-bottom: 711.4%; position: relative; bottom: 0; left: 0; background-image: url('data:image/jpeg;base64,'); background-size: cover; display: block;\"\n    ></span>\n    <img\n        class=\"gatsby-resp-image-image\"\n        style=\"width:100%;height:100%;margin:0;vertical-align:middle;position:absolute;top:0;left:0;box-shadow:inset 0px 0px 0px 400px transparent;\"\n        alt=\"3\"\n        title=\"\"\n        src=\"/static/8e413ac72d386ae480e9785726ced234/877ff/3.jpg\"\n        srcset=\"/static/8e413ac72d386ae480e9785726ced234/d2504/3.jpg 500w,\n/static/8e413ac72d386ae480e9785726ced234/877ff/3.jpg 1000w\"\n        sizes=\"(max-width: 1000px) 100vw, 1000px\"\n      />\n  </span></p>\n<p><span\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-wrapper\"\n    style=\"position: relative; display: block;  max-width: 1000px; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto;\"\n  >\n    <span\n      class=\"gatsby-resp-image-background-image\"\n      style=\"padding-bottom: 57.099999999999994%; position: relative; bottom: 0; left: 0; background-image: url('data:image/jpeg;base64,'); background-size: cover; display: block;\"\n    ></span>\n    <img\n        class=\"gatsby-resp-image-image\"\n        style=\"width:100%;height:100%;margin:0;vertical-align:middle;position:absolute;top:0;left:0;box-shadow:inset 0px 0px 0px 400px transparent;\"\n        alt=\"2\"\n        title=\"\"\n        src=\"/static/83a430a213fec2871a159d0ff1a5dfa9/877ff/2.jpg\"\n        srcset=\"/static/83a430a213fec2871a159d0ff1a5dfa9/d2504/2.jpg 500w,\n/static/83a430a213fec2871a159d0ff1a5dfa9/877ff/2.jpg 1000w\"\n        sizes=\"(max-width: 1000px) 100vw, 1000px\"\n      />\n  </span></p>\n<p><span\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-wrapper\"\n    style=\"position: relative; display: block;  max-width: 1000px; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto;\"\n  >\n    <span\n      class=\"gatsby-resp-image-background-image\"\n      style=\"padding-bottom: 337%; position: relative; bottom: 0; left: 0; background-image: url('data:image/jpeg;base64,'); background-size: cover; display: block;\"\n    ></span>\n    <img\n        class=\"gatsby-resp-image-image\"\n        style=\"width:100%;height:100%;margin:0;vertical-align:middle;position:absolute;top:0;left:0;box-shadow:inset 0px 0px 0px 400px transparent;\"\n        alt=\"4\"\n        title=\"\"\n        src=\"/static/82566f202730077fbb9e55669be61158/877ff/4.jpg\"\n        srcset=\"/static/82566f202730077fbb9e55669be61158/d2504/4.jpg 500w,\n/static/82566f202730077fbb9e55669be61158/877ff/4.jpg 1000w\"\n        sizes=\"(max-width: 1000px) 100vw, 1000px\"\n      />\n  </span></p>","fields":{"prefix":"2011"},"frontmatter":{"title":"Momardi website","categories":"web ux design wordpress ghostjs gatsbyjs inverted open-source","cover":{"childImageSharp":{"resize":{"src":"/static/f1c8fc53f0fe115c99207e95b4ad647c/d927d/logo.jpg"}}}}}},"pageContext":{"slug":"/momardi/","source":"work"}}